your credit report

00:53:56.370 --> 00:53:59.990
because you're one month
behind-- 30 days behind.

00:53:59.990 --> 00:54:04.280
If you fall four to
five months behind,

00:54:04.280 --> 00:54:07.980
the bank files something
called a "lis pendens."

00:54:07.980 --> 00:54:10.320
A lis pendens is public record.

00:54:10.320 --> 00:54:13.180
You can go to the
courthouse and see everyone

00:54:13.180 --> 00:54:15.580
who's listed as a lis pendens.

00:54:15.580 --> 00:54:19.610
