in pre-foreclosure-- the bank,
in order to get that home,

00:55:38.090 --> 00:55:43.800
they have to go to the court
and follow rules and steps

00:55:43.800 --> 00:55:45.860
to get your home from you.

00:55:45.860 --> 00:55:51.620
To take a step back, when you
get a loan, you get a mortgage.

00:55:51.620 --> 00:55:55.030
A lot of people say, I'm
going to go get a mortgage.

00:55:55.030 --> 00:55:56.650
You don't get a mortgage.

00:55:56.650 --> 00:55:58.790
You give a mortgage.

00:55:58.790 --> 00:56:00.300
What is a mortgage?

00:56:00.300 --> 00:56:03.040
A mortgage is a promise--
it's collateral--

00:56:03.040 --> 00:56:04.670
it's a promise to pay.

00:56:04.670 --> 00:56:08.870
You're basically telling the
bank, you loan me this money,

00:56:08.870 --> 00:56:11.180
and I'm going to sign
this piece of paper

00:56:11.180 --> 00:56:15.560
that if I default on this loan,
you can have my house back.

00:56:15.560 --> 00:56:17.960
You can have my house.

00:56:17.960 --> 00:56:23.960
So within New York State,
there's judicial foreclosure.

