00:56:40.290 --> 00:56:43.440
Every state have
judicial foreclosure.

00:56:43.440 --> 00:56:46.620
Some states have a
non-judicial foreclosure.

00:56:46.620 --> 00:56:49.280
Non-judicial
foreclosure, New York

00:56:49.280 --> 00:56:51.220
is not a non-judicial
foreclosure.

00:56:51.220 --> 00:56:53.510
Judicial means that
in order for a bank

00:56:53.510 --> 00:56:55.780
to take your home, if
you're in pre-foreclosure,

00:56:55.780 --> 00:56:58.010
they have to go through
the court system.

00:56:58.010 --> 00:57:00.620
Non-judicial means they
can just send you a letter

00:57:00.620 --> 00:57:02.830
and says, give me back my house.

00:57:02.830 --> 00:57:06.640
Foreclosure means that
the time has passed,

00:57:06.640 --> 00:57:09.000
the bank has granted
them permission

00:57:09.000 --> 00:57:11.940
to take your home from you.

00:57:11.940 --> 00:57:12.730
